{"type": "article", "id": 21353, "title": "文件夹式的蜡烛包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-27T07:30:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153735rs8fvREo0PNCJbFn.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组蜡烛有一个木片做的灯芯，似乎有秘密信息隐藏在木片上。波兰的平面设计 For brands studio 根据蜡烛设计包装时保留了木片的元素，将盒子做成了信件夹的感觉。盖子和圆扣用了薄木片，需要转动绳子才能把它打开，有一份古典和优雅。有黑白两款，售价 45 欧元起，<a href=\"http://www.message-candles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150925Qo2tOlHWwhnRCvmU.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"698\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150926g7pTQ2wtfaMkY6V5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150927MxPCA93T6XptJvfj.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"698\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150928eTGpiyZd1kYJs3L4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.77407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}